00:18:50.432 --> 00:18:51.519
generation?
 

00:18:51.519 --> 00:18:54.220
Take a caterpillar and a moth.
 

00:18:54.220 --> 00:18:56.348
You have a caterpillar and its
one kind of organism,

00:18:56.348 --> 00:18:59.452
