00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:49.785
Rotting meat,
rotting food,

00:19:49.785 --> 00:19:53.221
so you do an experiment,
you go around and you find some

00:19:53.221 --> 00:19:54.910
road kill or something.
 

00:19:54.910 --> 00:19:59.665
They didn't really have cars
back then but--this is all late

00:19:59.665 --> 00:20:02.808
1600s, 1700s it changes at that
time.

00:20:02.808 --> 00:20:06.098
They take a dead animal and
maggots come out of it.

00:20:06.098 --> 00:20:08.377
Well what it is,
you can take the dead meat that

00:20:08.377 --> 00:20:11.164
you find around,
and put it in a jar and close

00:20:11.164 --> 00:20:13.392
