00:20:31.538 --> 00:20:33.720
Then you get a little
imaginative about it,

00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:36.970
and if you read the literature
from this era,

00:20:36.970 --> 00:20:39.506
which I haven't,
but there's a lot of books that

00:20:39.506 --> 00:20:41.450
do and tell you the juicy
tidbits.

