00:51:54.480 --> 00:51:56.119
Anybody know?
 

00:51:56.119 --> 00:51:58.730
Nobody--there's all this
fundamentalism in America and

00:51:58.730 --> 00:51:59.420
nobody here.
 

00:51:59.420 --> 00:52:02.389
Well what is the cycle of life
described in the Bible?

00:52:02.389 --> 00:52:06.134
This is common in literature;
any literature major should

00:52:06.134 --> 00:52:07.110
