00:52:07.110 --> 00:52:08.800
Dust to dust.
 

00:52:08.800 --> 00:52:11.268
You've--how many of you have
heard dust to dust?

00:52:11.268 --> 00:52:16.500
Yeah, or sometimes translated
as earth to earth,

00:52:16.500 --> 00:52:19.293
it's Genesis 2:7:
